		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You may have better results if you make the white pixels move in circles rather than from left to right.<br /><br /><img src="http://www.acs.psu.edu/drussell/Demos/waves/Water-v8.gif" alt="Image" />

		

		</td>
